query:
SELECT 
  COUNT(*) as total,
  SUM(screenshotUrls IS NOT NULL AND screenshotUrls != '[]' AND screenshotUrls != 'null') as has_screenshots,
  SUM(description IS NOT NULL AND description != '') as has_description,
  SUM(descriptionAr IS NOT NULL AND descriptionAr != '') as has_descriptionAr,
  SUM(aiSummary IS NOT NULL AND aiSummary != '') as has_aiSummary,
  SUM(aiSummaryAr IS NOT NULL AND aiSummaryAr != '') as has_aiSummaryAr,
  SUM(sampleData IS NOT NULL AND sampleData != '[]') as has_sampleData,
  SUM(sourceUrl IS NOT NULL AND sourceUrl != '') as has_sourceUrl,
  SUM(threatActor IS NOT NULL) as has_threatActor,
  SUM(breachMethod IS NOT NULL) as has_breachMethod,
  SUM(region IS NOT NULL) as has_region,
  SUM(latitude IS NOT NULL) as has_coords
FROM leaks;
